hadiths[82]{hadithnumber,arabic,bengali,english,french,indonesian,russian,urdu,grades,reference,international_number,narrator_chain,chapter_intro}:
"3857","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ مَعْدَانَ بْنِ عِيسَى،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا الْحَسَنُ بْنُ أَعْيَنَ،","","It was narrated that 'Imran bin Husain said:: The Messenger of Allah said: ""There is no vow to commit an act of disobedience and its expiation is the expiation for an oath."" Mansur bin Zadhan contradicted him in his wording.","","","","کعب بن مالک رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے عرض کیا: اللہ کے رسول! اللہ تعالیٰ نے مجھے صرف سچ کی وج","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif Muquf'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif Muquf'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3857","",""
"3858","قَالَ الْحَارِثُ بْنُ مِسْكِينٍ قِرَاءَةً عَلَيْهِ وَأَنَا أَسْمَعُ:‏‏‏‏ عَنْ ابْنِ الْقَاسِمِ،‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that 'Imran bin Husain said:: The Messenger of Allah said: ""There is no vow for the son of Adam with regard to that which he does not possess, or to do an act of disobedience to Allah, the Mighty and Sublime."" 'Ali bin Zaid contradicted him -for he reported it from Al-Hasan from 'Abdur-Rahman bin Samurah.","","","","ابوہریرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  خیبر کے سال ہم لوگ رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے ساتھ تھے، ہمیں","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3858","",""
"3859","أَخْبَرَنَا يُونُسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْأَعْلَى،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ وَهْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أ","","It was narrated from 'Abdur-Rahman bin Samurah that the Prophet said:: ""There is no vow to commit an act of disobedience or with regard to that which the son of Adam does not possess.""","","","","عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس نے قسم کھائی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3859","",""
"3860","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ مَنْصُورٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ أَيُّوبَ،‏‏‏‏ عَ","","It was narrated that 'Imran bin Husain said:: The Messenger of Allah said: ""There is no vow to commit an act of disobedience or with regard to that which the son of Adam does not possess.""","","","","عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس نے قسم کھائی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3860","",""
"3861","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ سُلَيْمَانَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَفَّانُ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا","","It was narrated that Anas said:: ""The Prophet saw a man being supported by two others and said: 'What is this?' They said: 'He vowed to walk to the House of Allah.' He said: 'Allah has no need for this man to torture himself. Tell him to ride.'""","","","","عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما روایت کرتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس نے کسی ب","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3861","",""
"3862","أَخْبَرَنَا عِمْرَانُ بْنُ بَكَّارٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَيَّاشٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that Anas said:: ""The Messenger of Allah passed by an old man who was being supported between two men and said: 'What is the matter with him?' They said: 'He vowed to walk.' He said: 'Allah has no need for him to torture himself. Tell him to ride.'"" So he was told to ride.","","","","ابوہریرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  سلیمان بن داود علیہ السل","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3862","",""
"3863","أَخْبَرَنَا يُونُسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْأَعْلَى،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ وَهْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أ","","It was narrated that Anas bin Malik said:: ""The Messenger of Allah came to a man who was being supported by two others and said: 'What is the matter with him?' It was said: 'He vowed to walk to the Ka'bah.' He said: 'Allah does not benefit from his torturing himself.' And he told him to ride.""","","","","عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس نے قسم کھائی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3863","",""
"3864","أَخْبَرَنَا كَثِيرُ بْنُ عُبَيْدٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ حَرْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ الزُّبَ","","It was narrated that Abu Hurairah said:: ""The Messenger of Allah said: 'Whoever swears an oath and says: ""If Allah wills, then he has made an exception.""'""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا کہتی ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3864","",""
"3865","أَخْبَرَنَا يُونُسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْأَعْلَى،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ وَهْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أ","","It was narrated from Abu Hurairah, who attributed it to the Prophet:: ""Sulaiman said: 'I will certainly go around to ninety women tonight, each of whom will bear a child who will fight in the cause of Allah.' It was said to him: 'Say: If Allah wills' but he did not say it. He went around to them but none of them bore a child except for one woman who bore half a person."" The Messenger of Allah said: ""If he had said: 'If Allah wills,' he would not have broken his vow, and this would have been a means to help him to get what he wanted.""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا کہتی ہیں ک  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہوں","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3865","",""
"3866","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ الْمُخَرِّمِيُّ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَن","","It was narrated that Abu Sa'eed said:: ""When you hire a worker, tell him what his wages will be.""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا کہتی ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہو","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3866","",""
"3867","أَخْبَرَنَا إِسْحَاق بْنُ مَنْصُورٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا عُثْمَانُ بْنُ عُمَرَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Al-Hasan that he disliked to hire a man without telling him what his wages would be.","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گن","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3867","",""
"3868","أَخْبَرَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو صَفْوَانَ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ يُونُسَ،‏‏‏‏ عَنِ الزُّه","","It was narrated from Hammad -Ibn Abi Sulaiman- that he was asked about a man who hired a worker in return for food and he said:: ""No, not until he tells him (what his wages will be).""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا کہتی ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہو","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3868","",""
"3869","أَخْبَرَنَا هَارُونُ بْنُ مُوسَى الْفَرَوِيُّ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو ضَمْرَةَ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ يُ","","It was narrated from Hammad and Qatadah, concerning a man who said to another man:: ""I will lease (something) from you until I reach Makkah for such and such a payment, and if I travel for a month or such and such -something that he named- I will give you such and such in addition."" They did not see anything wrong with that, but they did not like it if he said: ""If I travel for more than a month I will deduct such and such from your lease.""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گن","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3869","",""
"3870","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيل التِّرْمِذِيُّ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَيُّوبُ بْنُ سُلَي","","It was narrated that Ibn Juraij said:: ""I said to 'Ata': 'What if I hire a slave for a year in return for his food, and for another year, in return for such and such?' He said: 'There is nothing wrong with that, and you may stipulate your conditions of hiring even for a few days.' 'How about if I make a deal to hire him when part of the year has passed?' He said: 'Do not hold me to account for what has passed.'""","","","","ام المؤمنین عائشہ رضی اللہ عنہا سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گن","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3870","",""
"3871","أَخْبَرَنَا هَنَّادُ بْنُ السَّرِيِّ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ وَكِيعٍ،‏‏‏‏ عَنِ ابْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ وَهُوَ عَلِيٌّ،‏","","It was narrated from Usaid bin Zuhair that he went out to his people, Banu Harithah, and said:: ""O Banu Harithah, a calamity has befallen you."" They said: ""What is it?"" He said: ""The Messenger of Allah has forbidden leasing land."" We said: ""O Messenger of Allah, what if we lease it in return for some of the grain?"" He said, ""No."" He said: ""We used to lease it in return for straw."" He said: ""No."" ""We used to lease it in return for what is planted on the banks of a stream that is used for irrigation."" He said: ""No. Cultivate it (yourself) or give it to your brother.""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہ کے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3871","",""
"3872","أَخْبَرَنِي عَمْرُو بْنُ عُثْمَانَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا بَقِيَّةُ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ أَبِي عَمْرٍو وَهُ","","It was narrated that Usaid bin Zuhair said:: ""Rafi' bin Khadij came to us and said: 'The Messenger of Allah has forbidden for you Al-Haql. Al-Haql is the third and the fourth. And Al-Muzabanah. Al-Muzabanah is to buy what is at the top of the date-palm trees in return for a certain number of Wasqs of dried dates.'""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت  ( گناہ کے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3872","",""
"3873","أَخْبَرَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ مَيْمُونٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مَعْمَرُ بْنُ سُلَيْمَانَ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ عَ","","It was narrated that Usaid bin Zuhair said:: ""Rafi' bin Khadij came to us and said: 'The Messenger of Allah has forbidden something that was beneficial for us, but obedience to the Messenger of Allah is better for you.  He has forbidden Al-Haql (renting land in return for one-third or one-quarter of the produce) to you, and says: Whoever has land, let him give it (to someone else to cultivate it) or leave it. And he has forbidden Al-Muzabanah. Al-Muzabanah means when a man has a lot of date-palm trees and another man comes and takes it in return for a certain number of Wasqs of dried dates.'""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  غضب کی نذر نہیں،","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3873","",""
"3874","أَخْبَرَنِي إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ يَعْقُوبَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا الْحَسَنُ بْنُ مُوسَى،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:","","It was narrated that Usaid bin Zuhair said:: ""Rafi' bin Khadij came to us and I was not sure what he meant. He said: 'The Messenger of Allah has forbidden to you something that used to benefit you, but obedience to the Messenger of Allah is better for you than that which benefits you. The Messenger of Allah has forbidden Al-Haql for you. Al-Haql means share-cropping the land in return for one-third or one-quarter (of the yield). So whoever has land that he does not need, let him give it to his brother (to cultivate it) or let him leave it. And he has forbidden to you Al-Muzabanah. Al-Muzabanah means when a man has a great number of datepalms and says: Take it in return for (a certain number of) Wasqs of dried dates this year.'""","","","","عمران رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  غضب کی نذر نہیں، اور اس کا","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3874","",""
"3875","أَخْبَرَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ،‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حَمَّادٌ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ مُحَمَّدٍ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ أَبِيهِ،‏‏‏‏ عَنْ عِم","","Usaid bin Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""Rafi' bin Khadij said: 'The Messenger of Allah has forbidden something for you that used to be beneficial for us, but obedience to the Messenger of Allah is more beneficial for us. He said: ""Whoever has land let him cultivate it, and if he is unable to do so, let him give it to his brother to cultivate.""'""","","","","عمران رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  غضب کی نذر نہیں، اور اس کا ک","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3875","",""
"3876","أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ وَهْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ سَلَمَةَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that Mujahid said:: ""I took Tawus by the hand and brought him to Ibn Rafi' bin Khadij, and he told him, narrating from his father, that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land. Tawus rejected that and said: 'I heard Ibn 'Abbas (say) that he did not see anything wrong with that.'""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ میں نے رسول اللہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3876","",""
"3877","أَخْبَرَنِي إِبْرَاهِيمُ بْنُ يَعْقُوبَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُسَدَّدٌ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَ","","(The previously mentioned chain) from Mujahid who said:: ""Rafi' bin Khadij said: 'The Messenger of Allah forbade us to do something that was beneficial for us, (but we respect and obey the command of the Messenger of Allah). He forbade us to lease land in return for some of its produce.""","","","","زبیر حنظلی سے روایت ہے کہ  ایک شخص نے ان سے بیان کیا کہ اس نے عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما سے ایک ای","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3877","",""
"3878","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ حَرْبٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو دَاوُدَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Prophet passed by the land of a man from among the Ansar who he knew was in need and said: 'Whose is this land?' He said: 'So and so's; he has given it to us in return for rent.' He said: 'Why did he not give it to his brother?'"" Rafi' came to the Ansar and said: ""The Messenger of Allah has forbidden something for you which was beneficial, but obedience to the command of the Messenger of Allah is more beneficial for you.""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت کی کوئی نذر","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3878","",""
"3879","أَخْبَرَنَا هِلَالُ بْنُ الْعَلَاءِ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو سُلَيْمٍ وَهُوَ عُبَيْدُ بْنُ ي","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Haql (renting land in return for one-third or one-quarter of the produce).""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت میں نذر نہی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Hadith'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3879","",""
"3880","أَخْبَرَنَا يَعْقُوبُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا هُشَيْمٌ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأ","","Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah came out to us and forbade something for us that had been beneficial for us. He said: 'Whoever has land, let him cultivate it or give it to someone else (to cultivate), or leave it.'""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  آدمی کی ایسی چی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Hadith'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3880","",""
"3881","أَخْبَرَنِي عَلِيُّ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ عَلِيٍّ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا خَلَفُ بْنُ تَمِيمٍ،‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Tawus and Mujahid, that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah came out to us and forbade something for us that had been beneficial for us, but the command of Messenger of Allah is better for us. He said: 'Whoever has land, let him cultivate it or leave it or give it (to someone else to cultivate).'""","","","","عبدالرحمٰن بن سمرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت میں کوئی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3881","",""
"3882","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ مَنْصُورٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّث","","It was narrated that 'Amr bin Dinar said:: ""Tawus regarded it disliked renting out land for gold and silver, but he did not see anything wrong with leasing it in return for one-third or one-quarter (of the yield). Mujahid said to him: 'Go to Ibn Rafi' bin Khadij and listen to his Hadith.' He said: 'By Allah, if I knew that the Messenger of Allah had forbidden that I would not have done it. But my Hadith comes from one who is more knowledgeable than him. Ibn 'Abbas (said) that the Messenger of Allah said: ""If one of you were to give his land to his brother (to cultivate it), that would be better than taking an agreed portion of the yield.""'""","","","","عمران بن حصین رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  معصیت میں کوئی نذ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3882","",""
"3883","أَخْبَرَنَا إِسْحَاق بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حَمَّادُ بْنُ مَسْعَدَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated from 'Ata' from Jabir, that the Messenger of Allah said:: ""Whoever has land, let him cultivate it. If he is unable to cultivate it, let him give it to his Muslim brother and not share-crop it with him.""","","","","انس رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے ایک شخص کو دیکھا کہ وہ دو آدمیوں کے بیچ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3883","",""
"3884","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا خَالِدٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّث","","Jabir said:: The Messenger of Allah said: ""Whoever has land, let him cultivate it or give it to his brother, and not lease it to him.""","","","","انس رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا گزر ایک ایسے بوڑھے شخص کے پاس سے ہوا ج","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3884","",""
"3885","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ حَفْصٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنِي أَبِي، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنِي إِب","","It was narrated that Jabir said:: ""Some people had some extra land which they leased out in return for half of the yield, or one-third, or one-quarter. The Messenger of Allah said: 'Whoever has land, let him cultivate it, or give it to his brother to cultivate or keep it (without cultivating it).'""","","","","انس بن مالک رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کا ایک ایسے شخص کے پاس سے گزر ہوا","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Hasan Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Hasan Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3885","",""
"3886","أَخْبَرَنَا نُوحُ بْنُ حَبِيبٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَ","","It was narrated that Jabir bin 'Abdullah said:: ""The Messenger of Allah addressed us and said: 'Whoever has land, let him cultivate it or give it to someone else to cultivate, and let him not rent it out.'""","","","","ابوہریرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  کہ رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جو شخص کسی بات کی قسم","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3886","",""
"3887","أَخْبَرَنَا الْعَبَّاسُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الْعَظِيمِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ، ‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Jabir who attributed it to the Prophet:: ""That he forbade leasing out land.""","","","","ابوہریرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  سلیمان علیہ السلام نے کہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3887","",""
"3888","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ حَاتِمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حِبَّانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَ","","It was narrated from Jabir that the Prophet forbade Al-Mukhabarah, Al-Muzabanah and Al-Muhaqalah, and selling fruit until it is fit to eat (ripe enough), except in the case of Al-'Araya.","","","","ابو سعید خدری رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  جب تم کسی مزدور سے مزدوری کراؤ تو اسے اس کی اجرت بتا دو۔","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3888","",""
"3889","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حِبَّانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا عَبْدُ ال","","It was narrated from Jabir that the Prophet forbade Al-Muhaqalah, Al-Muzabanah, Al-Mukhabarah and exceptions when selling, unless they were well-defined.","","","","حسن بصری سے روایت ہے کہ  وہ اس بات کو ناپسند کرتے تھے کہ کوئی آدمی کسی آدمی سے اس کی اجرت بتائے بغیر","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3889","",""
"3890","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ حَاتِمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حِبَّانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَ","","Jabir narrated that the Messenger of Allah said:: ""Whoever has land, let him cultivate it or give it to his brother to cultivate, and not lease it to his brother.""","","","","حماد بن ابی سلیمان سے روایت ہے کہ  ان سے ایسے شخص کے بارے میں پوچھا گیا جو کسی مزدور سے اس کے کھانے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3890","",""
"3891","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا حِبَّانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا عَبْدُ الل","","It was narrated from Jabir bin 'Abdullah:: ""The Prophet forbade Al-Haql and it is Al-Muzabanah.""","","","","حماد اور قتادہ سے روایت ہے کہ  ان سے ایک ایسے شخص کے سلسلے میں پوچھا گیا، جس نے ایک آدمی سے کہا: میں","{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3891","",""
"3892","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ حَاتِمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا حِبَّانُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَ","","It was narrated from Jabir bin 'Abdullah that the Prophet forbade Al-Muzabanah and Al-Mukhadarah. He (one of the narrators) said:: ""Al-Mukhadarah means selling fruit before it ripens and Al-Mukhabarah means selling grapes in return for a certain number of Sa's.""","","","","ابن جریج کہتے ہںي کہ  میں نے عطا سے کہا: اگر میں ایک غلام کو ایک سال کھانے کے بدلے اور ایک سال تک ات","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3892","",""
"3893","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا خَالِدٌ هُوَ ابْنُ الْحَارِثِ،","","It was narrated that Abu Hurairah said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.""","","","","اسید بن ظہیر رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  وہ اپنے قبیلہ یعنی بنی حارثہ کی طرف نکل کر گئے اور کہا: اے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3893","",""
"3894","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى وَه","","It was narrated that Abu Sa'eed Al-Khudri said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.""","","","","اسید بن ظہیر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمارے پاس رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ آئے تو کہا: رسول اللہ صلی","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Hasan'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Hasan'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3894","",""
"3895","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدّ","","It was narrated from Rafi' bin Khadij that the Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.","","","","اسید بن ظہیر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمارے پاس رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ آئے تو کہا: ہمیں رسول الل","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3895","",""
"3896","أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ قُدَامَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا جَرِيرٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ مَنْصُورٍ، ‏‏‏","","It was narrated from 'Uthman bin Murrah who said:: ""I asked Al-Qasim about Al-Muzara'ah, so he narrated from Rafi' bin Khadij that the Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.""","","","","اسید بن ظہیر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمارے پاس رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ آئے تو انہوں نے کہا، اور","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3896","",""
"3897","أَخْبَرَنِي إِسْحَاقُ بْنُ يَعْقُوبَ بْنِ إِسْحَاق الْبَغْدَادِيُّ أَبُو مُحَمَّدٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏","","Rafi' bin Khadij said that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land.","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے تمہیں ایک ایسی بات سے روک دیا","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3897","",""
"3898","أَخْبَرَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ حُجْرٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَنْبَأَنَا عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ يَعْنِي ابْنَ عَمْرٍو","","It was narrated that Abu Ja'far Al-Khatmi - whose name was 'Umair bin Yazid - said:: ""My paternal uncle sent me with a slave of his, to Sa'eed bin Al-Musayyab to ask him about Al-Muzara'ah. He said: 'Ibn 'Umar did not see anything wrong with it, until he heard the Hadith from Rafi' bin Khadij. Then he met him, and Rafi' said: ""The Prophet came to Banu Harithah and saw some crops. He said: 'How good are the crops of Zubair.' They said: 'It is not Zubair's.' He said: 'Is the land not Zubair's?' They said: 'No (it is not his), rather he is leasing it.' The Messenger of Allah said: 'Take your crops and give him what he spent.' So we took our crops, and gave him what he had spent.""","","","","مجاہد کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے طاؤس کا ہاتھ پکڑا یہاں تک کہ میں انہیں لے کر رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3898","",""
"3899","أَخْبَرَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو عَوَانَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ أَبِي حَصِينٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah, and said: 'Only three may cultivate: A man who has land which he cultivates; a man who was given some land and cultivates what he was given; and a man who takes land on lease for gold or silver.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  میں رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے ایک ایسی بات سے روک دیا ج","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3899","",""
"3900","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ سُلَيْمَانَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ عُبَيْدِ اللَّهِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا إِسْ","","It was narrated that Sa'eed said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah."" Sa'eed said: ""And he narrated something similar."" And Sufyan Ath-Thawri reported it from Tariq.","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم انصار کے ایک آدمی کی زمین کے پاس","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3900","",""
"3901","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏وَمُحَمَّدُ بْنُ بَشَّارٍ،‏‏‏‏ قَالَا:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا","","It was narrated that Tariq said:: ""I heard Sa'eed bin Al-Musayyab say: 'Cultivating land is not allowed except in three cases: Land which one owns, land which is given to one, or land which one rents in return for gold and silver.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے «حقل» سے منع فرمایا۔","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3901","",""
"3902","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ خَالِدٍ وَهُوَ ابْنُ الْحَارِثِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّ","","It was narrated from Sa'eed bin Al-Musayyab that the Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم ہماری طرف نکلے تو آپ نے ہمیں ایک","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3902","",""
"3903","أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ بْنُ خَالِدٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا حَجَّاجٌ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that Sa'd bin Abi Waqqas said:: ""At the time of the Messenger of Allah landowners used to lease their arable land in return for whatever grew on the banks of the streams for irrigation. They came to the Messenger of Allah and referred a dispute concerning such matters to him, and the Messenger of Allah forbade them to lease land on such terms, and said: 'Lease it for gold or silver.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہماری طرف رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نکل کر آئے تو ہمیں ایک","{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3903","",""
"3904","أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا زَكَرِيَّا","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""At the time of the Messenger of Allah we used to lease land on the basis of Al-Muhaqalah, so we would lease it in return for one-third or one-quarter of the yield, or a specified amount of food (produce). One day, a man among my paternal uncles came and said 'The Messenger of Allah has forbidden me to do something that was beneficial for us, but obedience to Allah and His Messenger is more beneficial for us. He has forbidden us to lease land on the basis of Al-Muhaqalah and to lease it in return for one-third or one-quarter of the yield, and for a specified amount of food (produce). And he commanded the landowner to cultivate it (himself) or to give it to someone else to cultivate. He did not like leasing it or anything else.'""","","","","عمرو بن دینار کہتے ہیں کہ  طاؤس اس بات کو ناپسند کرتے تھے کہ آدمی اپنی زمین سونے، چاندی کے بدلے کرا","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3904","",""
"3905","حَدَّثَنَا إِسْمَاعِيل بْنُ مَسْعُودٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا خَالِدُ بْنُ الْحَارِثِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَ","","It was narrated from Ayyub who said:: ""Ya'la bin Al-Hakim wrote to me (saying): 'I heard Sulaiman bin Yasar narrating from Rafi' bin Khadij, who said: ""We used to lease land on the basis of Al-Muhaqalah, leasing it in return for one-third or one-quarter of the yield, and a specified amount of food (produce).""'""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس کی کوئی زمین ہو تو وہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3905","",""
"3906","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ع","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""We used to lease land on the basis of Al-Muhaqalah during the time of the Messenger of Allah."" He said that one of his paternal uncles came to them and said: ""The Messenger of Allah has forbidden me to do something that was beneficial for us, but obedience to Allah and His Messenger is more beneficial."" We said: ""What is that?"" He said: ""The Messenger of Allah said: 'Whoever has land, let him cultivate it (himself) or give it to his brother to cultivate, and not lease it in return for one-third or one-quarter of the yield nor a specified amount of food (produce).'""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس کی کوئی زمین ہو تو وہ خود","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3906","",""
"3907","أَخْبَرَنَا هِشَامُ بْنُ عَمَّارٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ يَحْيَى بْنِ حَمْزَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا الْ","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""My paternal uncle told me that they used to lease land at the time of the Messenger of Allah in return for what grew on the banks of the streams, and a share of the crop stipulated by the owner of the land. But the Messenger of Allah forbade us that."" I (Hanzalah) said to Rafi': ""How about leasing it in return for Dinars and Dirhams?"" Rafi' said: ""There is nothing wrong with (leasing it) for Dinars and Dirhams.""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  بعض لوگوں کے پاس ضرورت سے زائد زمینیں تھیں جنہیں وہ آدھا، تہائی اور چ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3907","",""
"3908","أَخْبَرَنَا عِيسَى بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ وَهُوَ أَبُو عُمَيْرِ بْنُ النَّحَّاسِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏وَعِيسَى بْنُ يُونُس","","It was narrated that Hanzalah bin Qais Al-Ansari said:: ""I asked Rafi' bin Khadij about leasing land in return for Dinars and silver. He said: 'There is nothing wrong with that. During the time of the Messenger of Allah they used to rent land to one another in return for what grew on the banks of streams and where the springs emerged - some areas of which might give good produce and some might give none at all - and the people did not lease land in any other way. So that was forbidden. But as for leases where the return is known and guaranteed, there is nothing wrong with that.'""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہما کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمیں رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے خطاب فرمایا اور کہا:  جس کی کو","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3908","",""
"3909","أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ إِسْمَاعِيل بْنِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ يُونُسَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّ","","It was narrated that Hanzalah bin Qais said:: ""I asked Rafi' bin Khadij about leasing land. He said: 'The Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land.' I said: 'For gold or silver?' He said: 'No, rather he forbade leasing it in return for what the land produces. As for gold and silver, there is nothing wrong with that.'""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے زمین کو کرائے پر اٹھانے سے منع فرما","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3909","",""
"3910","أَخْبَرَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا الْمُفَضَّلُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏ع","","It was narrated that Hanzalah bin Qais said:: ""I asked Rafi' bin Khadij about leasing uncultivated land in return for gold and silver. He said: '(It is) permissible and there is nothing wrong with that. That is the due of the land.'""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع مخابرہ اور مزابنہ، محاقلہ سے او","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3910","",""
"3911","أَخْبَرَنِي زِيَادُ بْنُ أَيُّوبَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَبَّادُ بْنُ الْعَوَّامِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَال","","It was narrated that Rafi' bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade us to lease our land. At that time there was no gold nor silver. A man would lease his land in return for what grew on the banks of streams and where the springs emerged, and in return for something specific.""","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے محاقلہ و مزابنہ اور مخابرہ نامی بیع","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3911","",""
"3912","أَخْبَرَنِي أَحْمَدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو نُعَيْمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدّ","","It was narrated from Az-Zuhri that Salim bin 'Abdullah narrated something similar.","","","","جابر رضی اللہ عنہ بیان کرتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے فرمایا:  جس کی کوئی زمین ہو تو و","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3912","",""
"3913","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ إِدْرِيسَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو تَوْبَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ ح","","Salim bin Abdullah narrated that Abdullah bin Umar used to lease his land until he heard that Rafi bin Khadij forbade leasing land. Abdullah met him and said:: ""O Ibn Khadij, what do you narrate from the Messenger of Allah about leasing land?"" Rafi said to Abdullah: ""I heard two of my uncles, who had been present at Badr, telling the people in the house, that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land."" Abdullah said: ""I knew that at the time of the Messenger of Allah land used to be leased."" Then Abdullah was concerned that the Messenger of Allah had decreed something and he had not known about it, so he stopped leasing land.","","","","جابر بن عبداللہ رضی اللہ عنہما سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے «حقل»  ( تہائی، چوتھائ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3913","",""
"3914","أَخْبَرَنَا الثِّقَةُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا حَمَّادُ بْنُ مَسْعَدَةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ هِشَامِ بْنِ","","It was narrated that Az-Zuhri said:: ""We heard that Rafi bin Khadij used to narrate that his paternal uncles -whom he said had been present at Badr- (said) that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land.""","","","","جابر بن عبداللہ رضی اللہ عنہما سے روایت ہے کہ  نبی اکرم صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع مزابنہ اور مخاضرہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3914","",""
"3915","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ الرَّحْمَنِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ ح","","It was narrated from Shu'aib:: ""Az-Zuhri said: 'Ibn Al-Musayyab used to say: 'There is nothing wrong with leasing land in return for gold and silver, and Rafi bin Khadij used to narrate that the Messenger of Allah forbade that.''""","","","","ابوہریرہ رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع محاقلہ اور مزابنہ سے منع فرما","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Shadh'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3915","",""
"3916","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى وَه","","It was narrated from Ibn Shihab that Rafi bin Khadij said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land."" Ibn Shihab said: ""Rafi was asked after that: 'How did they lease land?' He said: 'In return for a set amount of food (produce), and it was stipulated that we would have whatever grew on the banks of the streams and springs.'""","","","","ابو سعید خدری رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع محاقلہ اور مزابنہ سے منع","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3916","",""
"3917","أَخْبَرَنَا زَكَرِيَّا بْنُ يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَزِيدَ بْنِ إِبْرَا","","Rafi bin Khadij told Abdullah bin Umar that his paternal uncles went to the Messenger of Allah, then they came back and told them that the Messenger of Allah had forbidden leasing arable land. Abdullah said:: ""We knew that he owned some arable land that he leased at the time of the Messenger of Allah in return for whatever grew on the banks of the streams of water, and for a certain amount of straw, I do not know how much it was."" Ibn Awn reported it from Nafi but he said: ""From some of his paternal uncles.""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے محاقلہ و مزابنہ سے منع فرم","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3917","",""
"3918","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو عَاصِمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّث","","It was narrated from Nafi':: ""Ibn 'Umar used to take rent for some land, then he heard something from Rafi' bin Khadij. He took me by the hand and went off to Rafi', and I was with him. Rafi' narrated to him from some of his paternal uncles, that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land, so 'Abdullah stopped (doing that) afterward.""","","","","عثمان بن مرہ کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے قاسم سے بٹائی پر کھیت دینے کے بارے میں پوچھا تو انہوں نے رافع بن خد","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3918","",""
"3919","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ قَالَ أَبُو عَاصِمٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ عُثْمَانَ بْنِ مُ","","It was narrated from Ibn 'Umar that he used to take rent for land until Rafi' narrated to him, from some of his paternal uncles, that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land. So he stopped doing that afterward.","","","","عثمان بن مرہ کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے قاسم سے زمین کرائے پر دینے کے سلسلے میں پوچھا تو وہ بولے: رافع بن خ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3919","",""
"3920","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ أَبِي جَعْفَ","","It was narrated from Nafi' that Ibn 'Umar used to lease out his arable land until he heard at the end of Mu'awiyah's Khilafah, that Rafi' bin Khadij used to narrate, that the Messenger of Allah had forbidden that. He went to him -and I (Nafi') was with him- and asked him (about that). He said:: ""The Messenger of Allah used to forbid leasing arable land."" So Ibn 'Umar stopped (doing that) afterward. When he was asked about it he said: ""Rafi' bin Khadij said that the Prophet forbade that.""","","","","ابوجعفر خطمی جن کا نام عمیر بن یزید ہے، کہتے ہیں کہ  میرے چچا نے مجھے اور اپنے ایک بچے کو سعید بن مس","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Lighairihi'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3920","",""
"3921","أَخْبَرَنَا قُتَيْبَةُ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أَبُو الْأَحْوَصِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ طَارِقٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَن","","It was narrated from Nafi' that 'Abdullah bin 'Umar used to lease arable land, then he was told that Rafi' bin Khadij narrated from the Messenger of Allah that he forbade that. Nafi' said:: ""He went out to him (and met him) in Al-Balat, and I was with him. He asked him (about that) and he said: 'Yes, the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing arable land.' So 'Abdullah stopped leasing it.""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع محاقلہ اور مزابنہ سے منع","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Hadith'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3921","",""
"3922","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ سُلَيْمَانَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ مُوسَى، ‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Nafi':: ""A man told Ibn 'Umar that Rafi' bin Khadij had narrated a Hadith concerning leasing of land. He and I, along with the man who had told him that, went to Rafi', and he told us that the Messenger of Allah had forbidden leasing land. So 'Abdullah stopped leasing land.""","","","","تابعی سعید بن مسیب کہتے ہیں کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع محاقلہ سے منع فرمایا ہے۔ سعید بن","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3922","",""
"3923","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ وَهُوَ ابْنُ مَيْمُونٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدٌ، ‏‏","","It was narrated from Nafi' that Rafi' bin Khadij told 'Abdullah bin 'Umar that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing arable land.","","","","طارق کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے سعید بن مسیب کو کہتے سنا: تین قسم کی زمینوں کے علاوہ میں کھیتی درست نہیں: و","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3923","",""
"3924","قَالَ الْحَارِثُ بْنُ مِسْكِينٍ قِرَاءَةً عَلَيْهِ وَأَنَا أَسْمَعُ:‏‏‏‏ عَنِ ابْنِ الْقَاسِمِ، ‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Nafi' that he narrated:: ""Ibn 'Umar used to lease his land in return for some of its produce.  Then he heard that Rafi' bin Khadij warned against that. He said: 'The Messenger of Allah forbade that.' He said: 'We used to lease our land before we came to know Rafi'.' Then he (Ibn 'Umar) became unsure, so he put his hand on my shoulder and we went to Rafi'. 'Abdullah said to him: 'Did you hear the Prophet forbid leasing land?' Rafi' said: 'I heard the Prophet say: Do not lease land in return for anything.'""","","","","تابعی سعید بن مسیب سے روایت ہے کہ  رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے بیع محاقلہ اور مزابنہ سے منع فرما","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3924","",""
"3925","أَخْبَرَنَا عُبَيْدُ اللَّهِ بْنُ سَعْدِ بْنِ إِبْرَاهِيمَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنِي عَمِّي، ‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated from Rafi' bin Khadij that the Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land.","","","","سعد بن ابی وقاص رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  کھیتوں والے لوگ رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے زمانے میں","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3925","",""
"3926","أَخْبَرَنِي زِيَادُ بْنُ أَيُّوبَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا ابْنُ عُلَيَّةَ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ أَن","","It was narrated that 'Amr bin Dinar said:: ""I heard Ibn 'Umar say: 'We used to sell grain before it was ripe and before it was evident that it was free of disease and blight (by means of Al-Mukhabarah). We did not see anything wrong with that, until Rafi' bin Khadij said that the Messenger of Allah had forbidden Al-Mukhabarah.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہم رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے زمانے میں زمین میں بٹائی ک","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Shadh'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Shadh'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3926","",""
"3927","أَخْبَرَنِي زَكَرِيَّا بْنُ يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عُبَيْدٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَال","","'Amr bin Dinar said:: ""I bear witness that I heard Ibn 'Umar asking about Al-Khibr (the agreement to Al-Mukhabarah) and he said: 'We did not see anything wrong with that, until Ibn Khadij told us earlier that he heard the Messenger of Allah forbidding Al-Khibr.'"" Hammad bin Zaid was in accord with the two of them.","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہم زمین میں بٹائی کا معاملہ کیا کرتے تھے، ہم اسے تہائی اور چو","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3927","",""
"3928","أَخْبَرَنَا إِسْمَاعِيل بْنُ مَسْعُودٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا خَالِدُ بْنُ الْحَارِثِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏ع","","It was narrated that 'Amr bin Dinar said:: ""I heard Ibn 'Umar say: 'We did not see anything wrong with Al-Khibr until last year, when Rafi' said that the Prophet of Allah forbade it.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہم رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم کے زمانے میں بٹائی کا معاملہ","{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3928","",""
"3929","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا حُجَيْنُ بْ","","It was narrated from Jabir bin 'Abdullah that the Prophet forbade leasing land.","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  میرے چچا نے مجھ سے بیان کیا کہ وہ لوگ رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3929","",""
"3930","أَخْبَرَنِي الْمُغِيرَةُ بْنُ عَبْدِ الرَّحْمَنِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عِيسَى هُوَ ابْنُ يُون","","It was narrated that Jabir said:: ""The Messenger of Allah forbade Al-Mukhabarah, Al-Muhaqalah and Al-Muzabanah.""","","","","حنظلہ بن قیس انصاری کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ سے دینار اور چاندی کے بدلے زمین کو","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3930","",""
"3931","أَخْبَرَنَا عَمْرُو بْنُ عَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا يَحْيَى، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا م","","It was narrated from Ibn 'Umar and Jabir that the Messenger of Allah forbade selling fruits until it was clear that they were free of blemish, and (he forbade from) Al-Mukhabarah; leasing land in return for one-third or one-quarter (of the yield).","","","","حنظلہ بن قیس کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ سے زمین کو کرائے پر دینے کے بارے میں پوچھ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3931","",""
"3932","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ بْنِ الْمُبَارَكِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ وَكِيعٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَ","","Rafi' bin Khadij narrated that the Messenger of Allah said to Rafi':: ""Do you rent out your arable land?"" I said: ""Yes, O Messenger of Allah. We rent it out in return for one-quarter, and in return for (a number of) Wasqs of barley."" The Messenger of Allah said: ""Do not do that. Cultivate it (yourselves), or lend it, or keep it.""","","","","حنظلہ بن قیس کہتے ہیں کہ  میں نے رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ سے سونے، چاندی کے بدلے صاف زمین کرائے پر","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3932","",""
"3933","أَخْبَرَنَا يَحْيَى بْنُ حَبِيبِ بْنِ عَرَبِيٍّ فِي حَدِيثِهِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏عَنْ حَمَّادِ بْنِ زَيْدٍ، ‏‏‏‏","","It was narrated that Rafi' said:: ""Zuhair bin Rafi' came to us and said: 'The Messenger of Allah forbade me to do something that was convenient for us.' I said: 'What was that?' He said: 'The command of the Messenger of Allah is true. He asked me: What do you do with your land? I said: We rent it out in return for one-quarter (of the yield) and a number of Wasqs of dates or barley. He said: Do not do that. Cultivate it, give it to someone else to cultivate, or keep it.'""","","","","رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمیں رسول اللہ صلی اللہ علیہ وسلم نے اپنی زمین کرائے پر دینے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Mauquf'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Mauquf'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3933","",""
"3934","أَخْبَرَنَا مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ يَحْيَى بْنِ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ ب","","It was narrated from Usaid bin Rafi' bin Khadij that the brother of Rafi' said to his people:: ""Today the Messenger of Allah has forbidden something which was convenient for you, but following his command is an act of obedience (to Allah) and is good. He forbade Al-Haql.""","","","","زہری سے روایت ہے کہ  سالم بن عبداللہ نے کہا، اور پھر اسی طرح روایت بیان کی، اور  ( اس روایت میں )  ع","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3934","",""
"3935","أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ الْمَلِكِ بْنُ شُعَيْبِ بْنِ اللَّيْثِ بْنِ سَعْدٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا أ","","It was narrated that 'Abdur-Rahman bin Hurmuz said:: ""I heard Usaid bin Rafi' bin Khadij Al-Ansari say that they did not allow Al-Muhaqalah, which is land that is cultivated in return for some of its produce.""","","","","سالم بن عبداللہ بیان کرتے ہیں کہ  عبداللہ بن عمر رضی اللہ عنہما اپنی زمین کرائے پر اٹھاتے تھے، یہاں","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3935","",""
"3936","أَخْبَرَنِي مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ خَالِدِ بْنِ خَلِيٍّ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا بِشْرُ بْنُ شُعَيْبٍ، ‏","","'Eisa bin Sahl bin Rafi' bin Khadij narrated:: ""I was an orphan in the care of my grandfather Rafi' bin Khadij. I reached puberty and became a man, and I performed Hajj with him. My brother 'Imran bin Sahl bin Rafi' bin Khadij came and said: 'O my father, we have leased our land to so and so (a woman) for two hundred Dirhams.' He said: 'O my son, leave that (do not do it), for Allah will give you other provision. The Messenger of Allah forbade leasing land.'""","","","","زہری کہتے ہیں کہ  ہمیں یہ بات پہنچی ہے کہ رافع بن خدیج رضی اللہ عنہ اپنے دو چچاؤں سے جو ان کے خیال","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3936","",""
"3937","أَخْبَرَنَا أَحْمَدُ بْنُ مُحَمَّدِ بْنِ الْمُغِيرَةِ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَالَ:‏‏‏‏ حَدَّثَنَا عُثْمَانُ بْنُ سَ","","It was narrated that 'Urwah bin Az-Zubair said:: ""Zaid bin Thabit said: 'May Allah forgive Rafi' bin Khadij. By Allah, I have more knowledge of the Hadith than him. We were two men who fought and the Messenger of Allah said: If this is how it is between you, then do not lease land. And he only heard the words: Do not lease land.'""","","","","زہری کہتے ہیں کہ  سعید بن مسیب کہتے تھے: سونے اور چاندی کے بدلے زمین کرائے پر اٹھانے میں کوئی مضائقہ","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Daif'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Daif'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3937","",""
"3938","قَالَ الْحَارِثُ بْنُ مِسْكِينٍ قِرَاءَةً عَلَيْهِ وَأَنَا أَسْمَعُ:‏‏‏‏ عَنِ ابْنِ وَهْبٍ، ‏‏‏‏‏‏قَ","","Ibn 'Awn said:: ""Muhammad used to say: 'In my view land is like the wealth put into a Mudarabah (limited partnership) contract. Whatever is valid with regard to the wealth put into a Mudarabah partnership, is valid with regard to land, and whatever is not valid with regard to the wealth put into a Mudarabah partnership, then it is not valid with regard to land.'"" He said: ""He did not see anything wrong with giving all of his land to the plowman on the basis that he would work with it himself, or with his children, and helpers, and oxen, and, that he would not spend anything on it; all expenses were to be paid by the owner of the land.""","","","","۱؎: یعنی شعیب کی موافقت کی ہے اور یہ موافقت اس طرح ہے کہ زھری اور رافع کے درمیان سالم کا ذکر نہیں ہے","{'name': 'Abu Ghuddah', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'},{'name': 'Al-Albani', 'grade': 'Sahih Isnaad Maqtu'}","Book 0, Hadith 0","3938","",""